Certainty	#474.	 questionless, doubtless. authoritative, authentic, official. sure as fate, sure as death and taxes, sure as a gun. evident, self-evident, axiomatic
Demonstration	#478.	 evident &c.. deducible, consequential, consectary, inferential, following. [demonstrated to one's satisfaction] convincing, cogent, persuasive (believable). Adv. of course, in consequence, consequently, as a matter of course
Manifestation	#525.	 obvious, evident, unmistakable, indubitable, not to be mistaken, palpable, self-evident, autoptical
